[
  {
    "startTime": 0.266,
    "endTime": 1.434,
    "text": "Now I thought I'd share some of my favorite"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.434,
    "endTime": 3.303,
    "text": "fitness fail stories from you guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.303,
    "endTime": 7.439,
    "text": "This first one is from @TuckerSolteszta."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.44,
    "endTime": 9.776,
    "text": "He says"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.8,
    "endTime": 14.3,
    "text": "My friend's dad bought a treadmill and told me, \"It's just for show when guests come over.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.347,
    "endTime": 15.482,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.482,
    "endTime": 18.118,
    "text": "This one's from @NikkiNombre."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.118,
    "endTime": 20.119,
    "text": "She says"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.2,
    "endTime": 23.0,
    "text": "I bought the TRX suspension training system from the TRX website."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.0,
    "endTime": 28.0,
    "text": "It was the only time my credit card company has ever contacted me with a potential fraud alert."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.828,
    "endTime": 30.163,
    "text": "\"Uh, this can't be right.''"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.163,
    "endTime": 32.532000000000004,
    "text": "''You would never order something like this, would you?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.531,
    "endTime": 34.333,
    "text": "-\"You got a lot of Dunkin' on here.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.602,
    "endTime": 38.671,
    "text": "This one's from @zgholloway."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.671,
    "endTime": 40.64,
    "text": "He says"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.7,
    "endTime": 43.0,
    "text": "On a recent trip to the gym, I dropped the bar and hit myself in the face while benching."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.0,
    "endTime": 50.0,
    "text": "No one came to help, so I had to roll the bar down my entire body until I got to a point where I could lift it off myself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.154,
    "endTime": 58.224000000000004,
    "text": "The old steamroller moves."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.224,
    "endTime": 60.592999999999996,
    "text": "This one's from @jeanneredden."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.593,
    "endTime": 62.695,
    "text": "She said"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.3,
    "endTime": 66.0,
    "text": "I couldn't afford a personal trainer so I followed a lady and her trainer around the circuit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.0,
    "endTime": 69.0,
    "text": "She asked, \"Are you copying me?\" I answered, \"Are you copying me?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.106,
    "endTime": 74.44,
    "text": "It's a standoff."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.77,
    "endTime": 79.345,
    "text": "This one's from @pascuamy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.345,
    "endTime": 81.481,
    "text": "She says"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.0,
    "endTime": 83.0,
    "text": "My husband once tried to follow the \"Body For Life\" diet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.0,
    "endTime": 87.0,
    "text": "Day 1, I saw him eating cookies and I commented that it wasn't his \"free day.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.0,
    "endTime": 91.0,
    "text": "He explained that he'd decided to break his free day up into small chunks of time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.425,
    "endTime": 94.194,
    "text": "Hour here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.194,
    "endTime": 95.562,
    "text": "Hour there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.562,
    "endTime": 96.996,
    "text": "I'll do three hours now of free time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.996,
    "endTime": 98.363,
    "text": "Yeah, I'm gonna eat this pizza here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.364,
    "endTime": 100.266,
    "text": "And then I've got 21 more hours left."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.266,
    "endTime": 102.66900000000001,
    "text": "Every week, baby"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.669,
    "endTime": 106.439,
    "text": "This one's from @laurabutler81. She says..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.5,
    "endTime": 110.0,
    "text": "I was on the treadmill and wanted to take my sweater off, so I tried to do it while running."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.0,
    "endTime": 114.0,
    "text": "I ended up with it stuck over my head, arms in the air, unable to stop running."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.851,
    "endTime": 123.289,
    "text": "\"Somebody stop and help me! Somebody help me!\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.289,
    "endTime": 124.624,
    "text": "\"It's just for show.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.624,
    "endTime": 126.259,
    "text": "\"It's just for show.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.259,
    "endTime": 128.561,
    "text": "This last one's from @debraweber5."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.561,
    "endTime": 130.73000000000002,
    "text": "She said..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.8,
    "endTime": 134.20000000000002,
    "text": "My sister bought a NordicTrack. It sat there so long and lonely that her kids renamed it \"Ignordic Track.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.2,
    "endTime": 135.969,
    "text": "There you go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.969,
    "endTime": 138.37,
    "text": "Those are some of the \"Tonight Show\" Hashtags from you guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.905,
    "endTime": 140.206,
    "text": "Check out more of our favorites."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.206,
    "endTime": 144.177,
    "text": "Go to tonightshow.com/hashtags."
  }
]